➜湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：七步成诗·听一朵花的心声（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/425801776_100115135	42726
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201019/febd6ba0f5a5405485d77a2505ae490a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七步成诗·听一朵花的心声</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣（武汉）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一朵花在呢喃自语</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">风传过她的心声</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花开不为落谁家</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只愿意把美丽献给春天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">献给大地，对她笑的人间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不做宫廷里的景</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不和别人争宠</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当皇贵妃有什么好呢</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">提心吊胆欢喜不够惹人争风吃醋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只愿自由在幽境里放香</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201019/7dd5673378814ed3b4c3feba64b228cf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
