➜凤萍（香港）：海水是潮湿的枕巾
http://www.sohu.com/a/425803023_100115135	43023
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201019/67d981db4e5f4bac825645266a45aa04.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>海水是潮湿的枕巾</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/凤萍（香港）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">担忧和空虚都很寂寞</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">思念静止在千里之外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">碧空的秋阳透过皮肤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在我的心里燃烧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>时间每转动一下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>都刻下新的印记</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>你用微弱的引力拉扯着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我以搁浅纪念消失的潮汐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">常梦见我和你在海里游泳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">身边总是多一尾鱼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鱼儿向我发出敌意的目光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无数次我从声频里惊醒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>海水是潮湿的枕巾</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>眼帘处划一道咸味的痕迹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>喝过海水的喉咙很干渴</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>嘴唇干裂似粘满盐粒</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
