➜苏坛：《草原的夜色》
http://www.sohu.com/a/425804804_100115135	43383
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201019/4a8fea330f414736afae4d179d47c0b3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《草原的夜色》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">草原的夜色</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有牛粪的味道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蒙古包也会寂寞无聊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天上的星星闪动一下</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">蒙古姑娘的脸红了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>牛奶依然那么鲜膻</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不过我还是喜欢喝酥油茶</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我在草原长大</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>天上有白云，地下有羊群</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>没有草的味道，我无法入睡</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦中我遇见王昭君</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">圆月下她弹奏着琵琶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还有那匹白色的马</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如诉如泣的思乡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">伴着哀鸿传唱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20201019/dbb89437ce394939a3e08818c686754e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
