➜广西诗人陈熠明：日正青山自远高
http://www.sohu.com/a/425806033_100115135	43777
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201019/7aa240aa1fab431888766ec87a639a21.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>日正青山自远高</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(一)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·登高只为近霞云</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相约万里天门外，马岭山中望远君。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">起步前程追日月，登高只为近霞云。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(二)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·流云眷恋马头山</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">登高与你秀峰峦，志向东潮玉水湾。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">荡远清风游梦外，流云眷恋马头山。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>(三)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝·羡慕红鹰自在飞</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>诗文作者·陈熠明</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">日照青山登远上，相邀与你共相陪。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长风故里流云外，羡慕红鹰自在飞。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201019/38363094a6f241629f655ab26c628b1f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
